now, as you know, all the armed forces Agencies 
have been forced by legislation

20:30.083 --> 20:38.537
to support only mission-oriented. They've been 
able to prove that the research that you do with

20:38.977 --> 20:51.077
support from the armed forces is clearly 
mission-oriented. And that's fine. They need for

20:51.738 --> 20:57.627
security and defense and attack. Because it's 
also called defense. Specific information. And

21:03.778 --> 21:12.351
it seems to me that's one of the purposes of the 
institutions of the country to provide what the

21:03.778 --> 21:12.351
government legitimately needs. But it's 
important to keep that, I think, separate from

21:13.513 --> 21:20.063
scientific activities. And again, it's groups 
that has been done insofar as all these

21:20.244 --> 21:26.854
mission-oriented activities are kept in a 
separate organization and separate from the

21:27.880 --> 21:30.343
campus. This was not done on an absolutely 
voluntary basis, although the separation has

