always been partially done. It was largely 
catalyzed by the student protest during the 60s.

21:43.642 --> 21:45.905
At the University of California San Diego? Right. 
And I think that's when classified research

21:48.028 --> 21:53.115
stopped being done, is that correct? When it 
stopped being done on campus. It's still being

21:55.876 --> 21:59.681
done to a quite large extent off campus.

