phrase. Again, you see Scripps Institution of 
Oceanography, then. You see their job as a

23:06.646 --> 23:12.732
combination of work in military, private 
enterprise, and private sciences. If you should

23:12.792 --> 23:18.858
like a public institution serving all three 
sectors of society. No, I think that... Scripps as

