23:50.390 --> 24:02.226
university. So that's very important, of course, 
that you deprive the taxpayers of the service that

24:02.647 --> 24:11.639
you have to give them. And particularly since most 
people use the proceeds of consultation for their

24:13.261 --> 24:20.110
own personal income, and more rarely for the 
benefit of the university. Now, when you came

24:26.974 --> 24:31.019
here, Roger Revelle was the director. Is that 
correct? Yes. And he remained director until he

24:32.621 --> 24:37.186
actually went off to Harvard. He sort of wore two 
hats here for a while. That's true. OK. Have you

24:40.931 --> 24:48.780
noticed any abrupt change between the direction 
of the institution under Revelle and then after

