his successors? No, no, everybody's tried to do 
the best they can, they could, in their own way, and

24:50.060 --> 25:01.650
each one of the directors have contributed very 
great things. For example, again, Roger Wells'

25:02.911 --> 25:19.746
greatness were particularly in the tremendous 
inspiration that he gave to everybody and his

25:02.911 --> 25:19.746
ability to

