28:27.909 --> 28:35.999
been rather advanced in the field. The USSR has 
been lagging behind, but I think it is coming up

28:37.280 --> 28:42.387
again. But the US has certainly, the United States 
have been leading in this because of their leading

28:42.427 --> 28:48.895
role both in software and hardware development. 
